    "Each mode has advantages and disadvantages that depend on the use case and context.",
    "AI is a continuously evolving topic that necessitates high-value human resources and demands the immediate deployment of relevant skills (Berente et al., 2021).",
    "As such, the internal mode of \"acquisition\" (i.e., employing new personnel) is particularly appropriate and a viable focus when investigating HR-related AI implementation ability (Lepak & Snell, 1999).",
